Description:
Prime Location - Huge Potential - Rare Opportunity !!!
Situated in the most prestigious part of St.Albans with excellent access to local amenities, this spacious property offers homebuyers and vigilant investors a rare opportunity with great potential. Redevelopment options (STCA) include retaining/renovating the existing home and building a brand new dwelling on an allotment of approximately 610m2 or demolishing and building a multi unit development site at a fantastic location. You can´t go wrong, but reap the rewards of this smart investment in a highly sought after pocket of the suburb.
Interior consists of two decent size bedrooms, spacious lounge room, central bathroom, kitchen with gas appliances alongside the dining room, opening to a sunroom comprising the laundry. Complemented with ample storage, natural timber floors lies all across.
Beautifully landscaped low maintenance backyard has plenty of room for outdoor living, an undercover verandah, a peaceful gazebo area, a shed for extra storage and an undercover veggie garden.
You have everything you need at a short walking distance such as the Alfrieda Street Shopping Strip (220m approx.), St.Albans Main Road Marketplace and St.Albans Community Centre (450m approx.), St.Albans Train Station (550m approx.), St.Albans Secondary College (950m approx.), St.Albans East Primary School (1km approx.), Victoria University (1.5km approx.) with numerous cafes/restaurants, parks and easy access to the Western Ring Road.
Contact C.Burak Binatli on 0455 663 331 to book in for an inspection today!!!
- Full of potential to develop (STCA) or renovate
- Decent block size of 610sqm approx.
- Fantastic location,within the shopping precinct
- Super convenience, surrounded by amenities
- Walking distance to train station,local transport
- A short stroll to schools,cafes,parks,etc
- Spacious, neat backyard and outdoor living area
- Easy access to Freeway, Western Ring Road
View this magnificent property now!Won´t last long

Description:
Under Offer
***This property is available for inspection by appointment-Please contact us to arrange a suitable time****
Delivering a luxurious lifestyle in the heart of Keilor East, this as-new home is set to impress with its freestanding construction, family-focused floorplan and premium features from start to finish. Meticulously detailed, the home's stunning interior showcases four generous bedrooms (large master) all with fitted robes, deluxe ensuite and equally-stylish main bathroom - both with first-class fittings and floor-to-ceiling tiles. Add to this a separate lounge/retreat (upstairs) and wonderfully spacious open-plan living/dining area further enhanced by a sensational stone-bench kitchen complete with Smeg appliances (dishwasher, oven and induction cooktop), breakfast bar and tiled splashback/feature wall. Square-set ceilings throughout, the home also includes zoned ducted heating and refrigerated cooling, alarm and CCTV, ducted vacuum, double-glazed windows, plus guest powder room (third WC), large laundry and under-stair storeroom. Step outside to a paved al-fresco entertaining area and private back garden, as well as the added appeal of remote-control double garage with internal entry. Walking distance to primary and secondary schools (including PEGS), Centreway shops and cafes, close to the soon-to-be-rebuilt Keilor East Leisure Centre, local parks and Steele Creek trails, public transport and easy freeway access.
*** COVID-19 Announcement ***
If you're attending a Private Appointment, we request that you only attend if you are fit and healthy to do so and not under any self-isolation conditions. We request that you maintain a healthy distance from our team members, and if requested wait outside until the property is ready for the appointment. Lastly, please refrain from touching items/fixtures and doors within the properties. If you would like to view something in particular, please request the agent's assistance. Thank you.

Description:
Under offer
***Inspection By Private Appointment Only***
Expressions of Interest Close 17th April at 5pm.
Beyond the attractive rendered facade, this impeccable single-level home presents an idyllic family lifestyle opportunity with its generous floorplan, long list of features and substantial garden surrounds. Occupying a wide block of land, the home's impressive interior comprises three bedrooms (extra-large master) along with a modern central bathroom complete with frameless shower, freestanding bath and floor-to-ceiling tiles. Adding to its family credentials is a spacious front lounge leading through to the open dining area and contemporary-style kitchen with stainless steel cooking appliances and dishwasher. Along with ducted heating, split-system air conditioning and additional wood heater, the home also includes CCTV, keyless entry and motorized security shutters, NBN connection and family-sized laundry. Step outside discover a large al-fresco style entertaining area and backyard garden with lush lawn, plus the unique appeal of a tandem double garage/workshop and additional front double carport via gated driveway (remote-controlled). Walking distance to local buses and popular Fosters Road shopping village, it's also close to a range of schools, acres of parkland and Keilor Park's world-class sports facilities, as well as easy access to the Calder Freeway.
*** COVID-19 Announcement ***
If you're attending a Private Appointment, we request that you only attend if you are fit and healthy to do so and not under any self-isolation conditions. We request that you maintain a healthy distance from our team members, and if requested wait outside until the property is ready for the appointment. Lastly, please refrain from touching items/fixtures and doors within the properties. If you would like to view something in particular, please request the agent's assistance. Thank you.

One-of-a-kind, this amazing home - complete with pool - delivers a vivid mix of indoor/outdoor space and style complemented by the finest fittings and fixtures throughout. Fully Renovated Family Abode
Upside Zero Contact Policy
In the wake of COVID-19, Upside Realty has implemented strict new procedures for all buyer inspections, as follows:
- No multiple-buyer open for inspections

Nothing left to do but simply move in, this stunning family home offers 4 spacious bedrooms with built-in robes, and a master with a full ensuite and walk-in robe.
Positioned in the heart of St Albans and situated within minutes to St Albans Markets, Sunshine Hospital, St Albans Train Station and with easy access to the Western Ring Road, location is the operative word here!
Whip up your favourite meals in the expansive and modern kitchen featuring quality appliances, a breakfast bar, stone benchtops and ample cabinetry.
Adorned with stylish floorboards throughout, LED downlights, and welcoming plenty of natural light for a warm and cosy feel, this fully renovated brilliance comes with space, comfort and liveability.
The rear of the home features a large rumpus room which makes for a great man cave or teenager's retreat.
Coupled with a low maintenance and private backyard, this property also includes multiple car park spaces for secure off-street parking.
One for the family, look no further! Call Nathan (Nghia) Chu on 0490049645 to organise your must-see inspection.

Description:
Inspection by Private Appointment
Smart, Spacious Family Living
Please ensure you also scroll through to the bottom of this ad to see our COVID-19 Property Inspection Policy!
Literally a few moments walk from Victoria University, schools, shopping and open parkland, this contemporary home offers dynamic lifestyle opportunities. Radiant sunshine from the north illuminates the length of the family dining and living with an alfresco backdrop to entertain easily among low-maintenance gardens.
_stained bamboo floors float openly through an expansive semi-formal lounge
_spaces for living and dining are drenched in magnificent sunlight and superbly proportioned
_geometric stone island/breakfast bar surrounded by generous kitchen cabinetry including walk-in pantry
_fabulous patio entertains undercover with attractively low-maintenance garden
_additional rumpus room upstairs offers a fabulous kids retreat
_arranged for up to five bedrooms all with fitted robes and a desirable amount of light
_three stylish bathrooms include an equally attractive ensuite to the master bedroom
_exceptionally generous storage throughout
_large laundry with external access
_ducted heating, cooling and double-glazed comfort throughout
_enjoy Kevin Flint Reserves green pathways and sparkling lake
_surrounded by a wide selection of schools and childcare
COVID-19 Property Inspection Policy
We take the health and well-being of our Team Members, Clients and the Community very seriously. Thats why weve developed a strict Condition of Entry Policy at our Inspections and Auctions, as follows:
_Social distancing of at least 1.5 mtrs from others
_No touching of any item or surface within the property
_Practicing good hygiene (with sanitisers, gloves and masks where available)
If you fall into any of the below categories, please just stay at home and have a rest!
_Are unwell with any flu-like symptoms
_Have been tested for and are awaiting results or have been confirmed positive for Covid-19
_Have been in contact with anybody who is being tested for or has been confirmed to have or have had Covid-19
_Have returned from overseas in the past 14 days
If you fall into these categories, rest assured, we are more than happy to give you a virtual property tour or make other arrangements instead. Just contact us to make arrangements!
